sentence: How many times has EECS 280 been offered ?
sentence-with-vars: How many times has department0 number0 been offered ?
sql: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.OFFERING_ID ) FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , COURSE_OFFERING AS COURSE_OFFERINGalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSE_OFFERINGalias0.COURSE_ID AND COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER = 280 ;
